lead_paragraph: A game drawn up to occupy some bored boys as winter approached at a Massachusetts gymnasium celebrates its 125th anniversary on Wednesday and basketball's status as the world's second most popular sport.

headline.print_headline: Basketball: From Humble Beginnings, Hoops Celebrates 125th Birthday
